  {%- if page.content != blank -%}
    {{ page.content }}
  {%- else -%}
    <h2>From our home to yours</h2>
    <p>Molly &amp; Sophie isn't a faceless big-box pet store — it's a small, family-run shop run from a cozy house with three goofy dogs underfoot. Every product we carry, we'd give to our own pack.</p>

    <p>We started this shop because we wanted to do <strong>two things</strong>: bring carefully chosen, genuinely good pet products to other pet parents, and quietly do some good along the way. That's why <strong>1% of every order</strong> is donated each month directly to a trusted pet rescue we believe in. We're not affiliated with or sponsored by any single charity — we hand-pick the rescue ourselves, every month, so we can keep helping the small organizations doing the biggest work.</p>

    <h2>Meet the inspiration</h2>
    <p><strong>Jack</strong> came to us after his previous owners traveled too often for work to give him the attention he needed. He spent a lot of time alone, often neglected. Today he's the calmest member of the pack and a sunbeam-finding expert.</p>
    <p><strong>Sophie</strong> was left behind during quarantine — her previous family said they couldn't keep her. Their loss became our luckiest day. She greets everyone like an old friend.</p>
    <p><strong>Molly</strong> lost her first home when her owners simply couldn't afford to care for her. She came to us scared and unsure — and turned into the goofiest little ball of sunshine you'll ever meet.</p>

    <blockquote>"Adopting a pet doesn't change the world, but for that one pet, the world changes forever."</blockquote>

    <h2>What we believe in</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Quality over quantity. We only stock products we'd give our own dogs.</li>
      <li>Pets are family. Period.</li>
      <li>Small businesses can do big good.</li>
      <li>Every animal deserves a soft place to land.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Thanks for being here. Thanks for shopping small. And thank you for helping us help the animals still waiting for their forever homes. 🐾</p>
    <p><em>— The Molly &amp; Sophie family</em></p>
  {%- endif -%}
</div>

